{"sectionId":767,"sectionIdLiteral":"767","humanId":"lesson-343","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"I am not asked to make a sacrifice to find the mercy and the peace of God.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 343"},"annotation":"W-343","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-343\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"767#1\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>The end of suffering can not be loss.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>The gift of everything can be but gain.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>You only give.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>You never take away.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>And You created me to be like You, so sacrifice becomes impossible for me as well as You.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#1:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>I, too, must give.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#1:7\"><span class=\"snr\">7</span>And so all things are given unto me forever and forever.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#1:8\"><span class=\"snr\">8</span>As I was created I remain.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#1:9\"><span class=\"snr\">9</span>Your Son can make no sacrifice, for he must be complete, having the function of completing You.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#1:10\"><span class=\"snr\">10</span>I am complete because I am Your Son.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#1:11\"><span class=\"snr\">11</span>I cannot lose, for I can only give, and everything is mine eternally.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"767#2\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>The mercy and the peace of God are free.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Salvation has no cost.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>It is a gift that must be freely given and received.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"767#2:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>And it is this that we would learn today.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"The end of suffering can not be loss. The gift of everything can be but gain. You only give. You never take away. And You created me to be like You, so sacrifice becomes impossible for me as well as","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 343: I am not asked to make a sacrifice‚Ä¶ | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to Lesson¬†343 ‚ÄúI am not asked to make a sacrifice to find the mercy and the peace of God‚Äù: The end of suffering can not be loss. The‚Ä¶","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"13. What Is a Miracle?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":764,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-a-miracle"]}},{"label":"Lesson 343","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":767,"slugs":["lesson-343","i-am-not-asked-to-make-a-sacrifice-to-find-the"]}}],"mobileBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"13. What Is a Miracle?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":764,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-a-miracle"]}},{"label":"Lesson 343","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":767,"slugs":["lesson-343","i-am-not-asked-to-make-a-sacrifice-to-find-the"]}}],"seoBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"A Course in Miracles","leadsTo":"dashboard"},{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part I